name: Naruto Mawaruze Futures
description:
839 × 839, 14 January 2020

Progress record to NFT OBJKT/202334 mint.

14 January 2020. That night I was lying in my hotel bed, selfishly fantasising about why Naruto was not used as an ingredient in the ramen I ate, and researching the history of Naruto.
While researching about Naruto, I came to a view and created a fragment of it.
I used African design and Afrofuturism as references.

Naruto Mawaruze Futures 

For some reason, I have recorded such a coined, provisional title in this fragment of my creation.
